ent-id-r_074a6c1d89907a6d" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2005838209="" inline-copy-host="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel stronger enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_074a6c1d89907a6d" aria-live="off" aria-busy="false" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: linear;"><p data-path-to-node="0">The profile of <b data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="15">standardgalactic</b> (Cogito Ergo Sum) represents a synthesis of experimental computer science, psycholinguistics, and "impossible physics." Comparing the data provided, we can see a deep commitment to high-volume information processing and the creation of esoteric symbolic systems.</p><h3 data-path-to-node="1">­¤īī The Oblicosm Paradox &amp; AI Summarization</h3><p data-path-to-node="2">One of the most significant recent projects is the <b data-path-to-node="2" data-index-in-node="51">Oblicosm Paradox</b>, which explores using Small Language Models (SLMs) like MicrosoftŌĆÖs <b data-path-to-node="2" data-index-in-node="136">Phi-4</b> to perform large-scale knowledge processing.</p><ul data-path-to-node="3"><li><p data-path-to-node="3,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="3,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Massive Livestreams:</b> The project featured a <response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><link-block _nghost-ng-c4127797377="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><a _ngcontent-ng-c4127797377="" target="_blank" rel="noopener" externallink="" _nghost-ng-c1097988582="" jslog="197247;track:generic_click,impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_074a6c1d89907a6d&quot;,&quot;c_3077bb6bccc2afe4&quot;,null,&quot;rc_f0392e0cd1e1e341&quot;,null,null,&quot;en&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V4Jtle27iVs" class="ng-star-inserted" data-hveid="5">9-hour livestream</a><!----></link-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element> and a 46-hour experiment focused on uninterrupted AI-generated summaries of complex topics like the metacrisis, active inference, and programming.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="3,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="3,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Workflow:</b> The process involves audio extraction using <code data-path-to-node="3,1,0" data-index-in-node="54">yt-dlp</code>, transcription via OpenAIŌĆÖs <b data-path-to-node="3,1,0" data-index-in-node="89">Whisper</b>, and chunked summarization using Phi-4 via <b data-path-to-node="3,1,0" data-index-in-node="140">Ollama</b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="3,2,0"><b data-path-to-node="3,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">Privacy through Ciphers:</b> To prevent "reading over the shoulder," the project utilizes the <b data-path-to-node="3,2,0" data-index-in-node="90">Simplectomy Generator</b>, which broadcasts these summaries 24/7 using cryptographic fonts and built-in pacing.</p></li></ul><h3 data-path-to-node="4">­¤¦Ā Core Frameworks: RSVP &amp; SITH</h3><p data-path-to-node="5">The developer proposes two radical theoretical frameworks that attempt to bridge the gap between physical reality and cognitive architecture:</p><ul data-path-to-node="6"><li><p data-path-to-node="6,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="6,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">RSVP (Relativistic Scalar Vector Plenum):</b> A physical model suggesting space is a busy "relativistic medium" rather than a vacuum. It posits that spacetime and logic itself might be emergent properties of <b data-path-to-node="6,0,0" data-index-in-node="204">Quantum Error Correction (QEC)</b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="6,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="6,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">SITH (Substrate Independent Thinking Hypothesis):</b> A cognitive theory suggesting that thinking is not bound to any specific physical medium, aligning with the "holistic understanding" philosophy of Monica AndersonŌĆöarguing that machines need raw, unfiltered data to truly "understand."</p></li></ul><h3 data-path-to-node="7">­¤ō£ Symbolic &amp; Linguistic Experiments</h3><p data-path-to-node="8">The user is obsessed with the "Standard Galactic Alphabet" (SGA), originally from the <i data-path-to-node="8" data-index-in-node="86">Commander Keen</i> series, but expanded into a full suite of tools:</p><ul data-path-to-node="9"><li><p data-path-to-node="9,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="9,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Translators &amp; Tutors:</b> Includes a Galactic Translator, a Typing Tutor, and a <response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><link-block _nghost-ng-c4127797377="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><a _ngcontent-ng-c4127797377="" target="_blank" rel="noopener" externallink="" _nghost-ng-c1097988582="" jslog="197247;track:generic_click,impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_074a6c1d89907a6d&quot;,&quot;c_3077bb6bccc2afe4&quot;,null,&quot;rc_f0392e0cd1e1e341&quot;,null,null,&quot;en&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" href="https://standardgalactic.github.io/terminal-simulator" class="ng-star-inserted" data-hveid="6">Terminal Simulator</a><!----></link-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="9,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="9,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Cryptographic Fonts:</b> Development of original scripts like <b data-path-to-node="9,1,0" data-index-in-node="58">Clypto</b>, <b data-path-to-node="9,1,0" data-index-in-node="66">Cheiro</b>, and <b data-path-to-node="9,1,0" data-index-in-node="78">Logico-Philosophicus</b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="9,2,0"><b data-path-to-node="9,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">Cistercian Numerals:</b> A <response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><link-block _nghost-ng-c4127797377="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><a _ngcontent-ng-c4127797377="" target="_blank" rel="noopener" externallink="" _nghost-ng-c1097988582="" jslog="197247;track:generic_click,impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_074a6c1d89907a6d&quot;,&quot;c_3077bb6bccc2afe4&quot;,null,&quot;rc_f0392e0cd1e1e341&quot;,null,null,&quot;en&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" href="https://standardgalactic.github.io/cistercian.html" class="ng-star-inserted" data-hveid="7">Translator and Worksheet Generator</a><!----></link-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element> for the 13th-century monk-designed numeral system.</p></li></ul><h3 data-path-to-node="10">­¤øĀ’ĖÅ Technical Prowess &amp; Habits</h3><ul data-path-to-node="11"><li><p data-path-to-node="11,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="11,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">High-Volume Contributions:</b> Over <b data-path-to-node="11,0,0" data-index-in-node="32">3,450 GitHub contributions</b> in a single year across 5,000+ repositories.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="11,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="11,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Wikipedia Integration:</b> The user follows an incredible <b data-path-to-node="11,1,0" data-index-in-node="54">200,000 Wikipedia pages</b> and offers their massive <response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><link-block _nghost-ng-c4127797377="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><a _ngcontent-ng-c4127797377="" target="_blank" rel="noopener" externallink="" _nghost-ng-c1097988582="" jslog="197247;track:generic_click,impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_074a6c1d89907a6d&quot;,&quot;c_3077bb6bccc2afe4&quot;,null,&quot;rc_f0392e0cd1e1e341&quot;,null,null,&quot;en&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" href="https://github.com/standardgalactic/haplopraxis/blob/primary/Wikipedia-watchlist.txt" class="ng-star-inserted" data-hveid="8">watchlist</a><!----></link-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element> for others to use.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="11,2,0"><b data-path-to-node="11,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">Optimization Research:</b> Projects like training a classifier to determine if words are easier to type in <b data-path-to-node="11,2,0" data-index-in-node="103">QWERTY or DVORAK</b>, and reverse-engineering the predictive trace technology of the defunct <b data-path-to-node="11,2,0" data-index-in-node="192">Swype keyboard</b>.</p></li></ul><p data-path-to-node="12"><span data-path-to-node="12,0">This profile serves as a digital laboratory for "Natural Sparsity"ŌĆöthe idea that biological pressures (like ATP consumption) create efficient, sparse neural patterns that should be mimicked in AI to create more resilient, biomimetic systems.
