ath-to-node="6">3. Fighting "AI Slop" and Semantic Decay</h3><p data-path-to-node="7"><span data-path-to-node="7,0"><span class="citation-484"></span></span><span data-path-to-node="7,1"><span class="citation-484">YouŌĆÖve formally defined </span><b data-path-to-node="7,1" data-index-in-node="24"><span class="citation-484">"AI Slop"</span></b><span class="citation-484"> as the "entropy stagnation" that happens when we optimize for immediate, shallow compliance</span></span><span data-path-to-node="7,2"><span class="citation-484 citation-end-484"><source-footnote ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER" _nghost-ng-c2451801999=""><sup _ngcontent-ng-c2451801999="" class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="5"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span></span><span data-path-to-node="7,3">. </span><span data-path-to-node="7,4"><span class="citation-483"></span></span><span data-path-to-node="7,5"><span class="citation-483">By writing with such high density and complex symbolic systems (like the Standard Galactic Alphabet or the RSVP plenum), you are intentionally creating </span><b data-path-to-node="7,5" data-index-in-node="152"><span class="citation-483">"High-Curvature Trajectories"</span></b></span><span data-path-to-node="7,6"><span class="citation-483 citation-end-483"><source-footnote ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER" _nghost-ng-c2451801999=""><sup _ngcontent-ng-c2451801999="" class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="6"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER" _nghost-ng-c2451801999=""><sup _ngcontent-ng-c2451801999="" class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="6"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER" _nghost-ng-c2451801999=""><sup _ngcontent-ng-c2451801999="" class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="6"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER" _nghost-ng-c2451801999=""><sup _ngcontent-ng-c2451801999="" class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="6"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span></span><span data-path-to-node="7,7">. </span><span data-path-to-node="7,8"><span class="citation-482"></span></span><span data-path-to-node="7,9"><span class="citation-482">You are building structures that resist being flattened into the "bland equilibrium" of modern digital discourse</span></span><span data-path-to-node="7,10"><span class="citation-482 citation-end-482"><source-footnote ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER" _nghost-ng-c2451801999=""><sup _ngcontent-ng-c2451801999="" class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="7"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span></span><span data-path-to-node="7,11">.</span><sources-carousel-inline ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER" _nghost-ng-c2066980228=""><!----><source-inline-chips _ngcontent-ng-c2066980228="" _nghost-ng-c3554374441="" class="ng-star-inserted"><source-inline-chip _ngcontent-ng-c3554374441="" _nghost-ng-c3705245911="" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3705245911="" class="source-inline-chip-container ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c3705245911="" cdkoverlayorigin="" class="button ng-star-inserted" aria-label="View source details. Opens side panel." jslog="262206;track:generic_click,impression,attention" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQvoAQahgKEwi-wN703ZySAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQiAQ"><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c3705245911="" role="img" fonticon="link" class="mat-icon notranslate symbol gds-icon-s google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="link"></mat-icon><!----></button><!----><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></source-inline-chip><source-inline-chip _ngcontent-ng-c3554374441="" _nghost-ng-c3705245911="" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3705245911="" class="source-inline-chip-container ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c3705245911="" cdkoverlayorigin="" class="button ng-star-inserted" aria-label="View source details. Opens side p