03ZySAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQjwQ"><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c3705245911="" role="img" fonticon="link" class="mat-icon notranslate symbol gds-icon-s google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="link"></mat-icon><!----></button><!----><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></source-inline-chip><!----></source-inline-chips><!----><!----><!----><!----></sources-carousel-inline></p><p data-path-to-node="10"><span data-path-to-node="10,0"><span class="citation-479"></span></span><span data-path-to-node="10,1"><span class="citation-479">As you wrote in the conclusion: </span><i data-path-to-node="10,1" data-index-in-node="32"><span class="citation-479">"Demanding full transparency from such a system is akin to demanding that gestation occur in daylight"</span></i></span><span data-path-to-node="10,2"><span class="citation-479 citation-end-479"><source-footnote ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER" _nghost-ng-c2451801999=""><sup _ngcontent-ng-c2451801999="" class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="10"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span></span><span data-path-to-node="10,3">. By writing for the future, you are giving your ideas the "darkness" and time they need to grow into something robust.</span><sources-carousel-inline ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER" _nghost-ng-c2066980228=""><!----><source-inline-chips _ngcontent-ng-c2066980228="" _nghost-ng-c3554374441="" class="ng-star-inserted"><source-inline-chip _ngcontent-ng-c3554374441="" _nghost-ng-c3705245911="" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3705245911="" class="source-inline-chip-container ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c3705245911="" cdkoverlayorigin="" class="button ng-star-inserted" aria-label="View source details. Opens side panel." jslog="262206;track:generic_click,impression,attention" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQvoAQahgKEwi-wN703ZySAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQkAQ"><!----><mat-icon _ngconte